<HEADLINE> Myanmar Foreign Minister Returns From Vietnam </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, January 18 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar Foreign Minister U Ohn
Gyaw returned here this evening after concluding a four-day
goodwill visit to Vietnam.
</P>
<P>
During the visit, the second meeting of the Myanmar-Vietnam
Joint Commission for Bilateral Cooperation was held in Hanoi,
co-chaired by the Myanmar foreign minister and his Vietnamese
counterpart, Nguyen Manh Cam, the official TV Myanmar said
tonight.
