<TEXT>
<P>
ZHUHAI, January 18 (Xinhua) -- More than 200 women from the
inland area and Hong Kong today pledged to help the smooth return
of Hong Kong to the motherland. They also vowed to work for the
region's prosperity and stability.
</P>
<P>
The women were attending a forum, the second of its kind, held
in Zhuhai in south China's Guangdong Province.
</P>
<P>
