Standing Committee of the National People's Congress, said that
under the banner of patriotism, women from all walks of life and
woman organizations in Hong Kong should strive to unite with their
sisters from various ethnic groups, social sectors and classes in
the inland areas.
</P>
<P>
She also expressed the hope that women in inland areas and Hong
Kong will continue to increase exchanges, and closely cooperate
with each other to create a bright future for Hong Kong, and make
greater contributions to invigorating the Chinese nation. 
