<HEADLINE> China, Cape Verde Sign Economic Agreement </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CIDADE DE PRAIA, January 17 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Foreign
Minister Qian Qichen held talks with his counterpart in Cape
Verde, Amical Spencer Lopes, today and the two signed an agreement
on economic and technological cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Qian, also Vice Premier of China, arrived at Didade de Praia
today at the invitation of the government of Cape Verde for an
official visit.
</P>
<P>
