over the smooth development of Sino-Cape Verde relations since the
two countries established diplomatic relations in 1976.
</P>
<P>
Amical Spencer Lopes said his country would stick to the "one
China" policy.
</P>
<P>
Qian expressed appreciation over Cape Verde's position and
promised that China would strengthen economic and trade ties with
it in accordance with the principle of equality and mutual
benefits. 
